{"tid":850263,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"最近發覺好多香港人都唔識講唔該。","createTime":"2018-10-06T10:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T01:55:47.000Z","uid":19889,"like":89,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2199252e86f5f682e7d939ba9dae60fa2546f56e","tid":850263,"uid":19889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"用第三者既角度睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近見到無論係幫人推住道門，又或者係服務性行業，例如清潔姐姐，餐廳收銀咁，好多人都係俾完錢就直接走左去。<br />\n<br />\n可能你覺得香港生活節奏快，唔似英國咁落巴士都講唔該。有可能你覺得佢哋打得份工就唔會與你講唔該，甚至佢哋都覺得冇乜所謂，打份工啫。<br />\n<br />\n但我個人認為只係講一句唔該，其實係一個應該有嘅表現。"},{"pid":"dfd00a5f6ac6deee942faa835f7c21c8d5477586","tid":850263,"uid":137703,"like":38,"dislike":3,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:49:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e919c8467b95d0e67cba515fd5538da70b5ad81a","tid":850263,"uid":52194,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:52:03.000Z","msg":"應該話<br />\n會講嘅人係習慣<br />\n講係應份唔講會比人小你無禮貌"},{"pid":"1aacb575b8068352d8d7293c71db5b334872b313","tid":850263,"uid":158145,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:52:56.000Z","msg":"我係唔該前唔該後"},{"pid":"f8634c502b4cc60e6c6baab824fc611a51b083bd","tid":850263,"uid":108756,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:54:17.000Z","msg":"我自己由細屋企人已經教要講 <br />\n身邊就好多人都無呢種意識去講"},{"pid":"22637b8d9be0e76bc2ad6dc833c19e7fc7440ab7","tid":850263,"uid":208726,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:54:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"659bbb277f93ae5bca3001d2391a378c0b9cda24","tid":850263,"uid":49853,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T10:55:11.000Z","msg":"快撚d啦唔該"},{"pid":"ac3a94f9488ccfa355403f1af1aab64e27f06f1e","tid":850263,"uid":19889,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"